selectStatements.query: SELECT CASE WHEN NOT EXISTS (SELECT PARAMETER_CODE FROM DW_CONTENT_PARAM_CONFIG WHERE PARAMETER_CODE='PARAM_ERP_FINANCIALS_CALENDAR_ID') THEN 'ABCTest123ABC' ELSE (SELECT NVL(PARAMETER_VALUE,'ABCTest123ABC') FROM DW_CONTENT_PARAM_CONFIG WHERE PARAMETER_CODE='PARAM_ERP_FINANCIALS_CALENDAR_ID') END AS PARAMETER_VALUE FROM DUAL
